OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDrier this
OL,6,Fevening with showers clearing
OL,7,Feastwards to leave late sunny spells.
OL,8,FTurning cloudier again overnight with
OL,9,Ffurther showers pushing through.
OL,10,FStaying mild and breezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CThursday:FSunny spells and scattered
OL,13,Fshowers on Thursday. Turning
OL,14,Fincreasingly cloudy through the
OL,15,Fafternoon with patchy outbreaks of
OL,16,Frain. Winds easing.
